ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 6th day of August, 2014, the “Appeal from the Denial of Motion to Hold Appeal,” treated as a Petition for Review, and the “Lawful Notification and Action Summary Judgment,” treated as an Application for Relief, are DENIED.
